precis:
Regulations Amending the DISCLOSURE OF INTEREST (AUTHORIZED FOREIGN BANKS)
REGULATIONS by specifying that banks in this category must provide a
customer who opens an interest-earning deposit account with a written
statement that sets out the rate of interest and how it is calculated.
